7:33.000Z","msg":"rambo打完越戰都變condom，除咗勝利係無野賠償到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實就梗係現兜兜唔好講咁多廢話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}